com.fortyoneconcepts.valjogen.model.util

Class AnnotationProxyBuilder<A extends Annotation>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fortyoneconcepts.valjogen.model.util.AnnotationProxyBuilder<A>
  • Type Parameters:
    A - The type of the annotation that this builder should construct
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    InvocationHandler

    public final class AnnotationProxyBuilder<A extends Annotation>
extends Object
implements InvocationHandler
    A fluent builder that creates a new instance of our annotation with defaults (works also with source-only annotations at runtime). Use add(attribute-method-name, value) to configure values on the attribute followed by the build method to generate an annotation instance.
